snippet.title: SM64 Sapphire - Release (Rom Hack)
snippet.description:
Download: https://drive.google.com/open?id=1c8EexfOxRnpzKEYEZrZQoqQGfxAtSTXe

30 stars spread amongst 4 main stages and 1 secret stage, plus a bowser stage to finish.

My intention with this hack was quality over quantity. Enjoy!
